title: 1328 Campbell Street, Oakland, CA
posting_body: ['Spacious 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom Unit in great West Oakland BART commuter location', 'OPEN HOUSE:', 'Sunday  12 pm to 5 pm', 'Call or Text', 'show contact info', 'Ext 207', 'Jonathan Fleming', '1328 Campbell Street', 'Oakland CA 94607', 'West Oakland living at its best!', 'This move-in-ready, one bedroom / one bathroom duplex unit offers a trendsetting modern lifestyle.', 'Featuring an updated contemporary kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and an updated contemporary bathroom, as well as a living room with a floor-to-ceiling built-in bookcase, a nice size bedroom with a spacious closet, versatile laminate flooring, and fresh paint.', 'This one/one duplex unit located in West Oakland is home to impressive views of the city skyline with direct access to transportation as well as close to plenty of on-trend restaurants, quaint coffee shops, and nearby attractions including Pardee Home Museum, Old Oakland, and Preservation Park.', 'If you’re looking for a stylish 1-bedroom 1-bath duplex unit for rent in a desirable West Oakland location, schedule your private tour of 1316 Campbell Street, by contacting <URL> today or by calling', 'show contact info', 'Ext 207.', 'Also, visit us at <URL>', 'The monthly rent is $1950, and the security deposit of $1950 equals $3900 total move-in amount.', 'Requirements and other details:', 'Rental History Verification', 'Legal Source of income', 'Credit Report Screening', '$40 Rental Screening fee, non-refundable', 'Water/Garbage paid by the landlord.', 'Tenants pay PGE']
